title: HUGE 2-bedroom, AVAILABLE NOW!!!
posting_body: ['Greentree Apartments – #M257', 'Available: NOW', 'Bedroom: 2', 'Bathrooms: 1', 'Rent: $1,462.00', 'Deposit:  $700.00', 'FREE Water/Sewer/Garbage', 'Laundry Facility In Each Building', 'Community Amenities:', 'Playgrounds', 'Small Animals Allowed (one time deposit and monthly pet rent)', 'Excellent Freeway Access', 'Storage Space', 'Free Parking Stall Included', 'Next to 19 Acre Park!', 'Application Fee: $42 (per adult)', 'Reservation Fee: $200 (goes towards Deposit)', 'Deposit: $700', '***Units Rent On A First Come First Serve Basis!!', 'Whichever APPROVED applicant that puts the reservation fee on the unit first, gets the unit!', '***', 'This Community has income restrictions you must be below to qualify:', '1-Person income must be less than $54,360', '2-Persons income must be less than $62,160', '3-Persons income must be less than $69,900', '4-Persons income must be less than $77,640', '5-Persons income must be less than $83,880', "With excellent maintenance and customer service you'll be glad you chose Park Hill and Greentree Apartments as your new home.", 'We are centrally located near The Landing, the light rail, downtown Renton and Westfield Southcenter.', 'Park Hill and Greentree Apartment Homes are conveniently located in a quiet wooded neighborhood and feature beautifully landscaped grounds.', 'A wide variety of spacious floorplans which offers each resident an opportunity to enjoy a truly unique environment.', 'Select units include free water, sewer & garbage, washer & dryers and fireplaces.', "Enjoy our children's play area.", 'Excellent freeway access and only minutes away from Boeing!', 'Office is open Monday - Friday 9am - 5pm, by Appointment ONLY!!!', 'Call our office TODAY to schedule a tour!!!']
